  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Retro gameplay, Retro difficulty!</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398430/extras/ce2b3349be9825e54b525cf17a3b067b.poster.avif?t=1762781813\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398430/extras/ce2b3349be9825e54b525cf17a3b067b.webm?t=1762781813\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398430/extras/ce2b3349be9825e54b525cf17a3b067b.mp4?t=1762781813\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Scurry across multiple lanes of traffic, hatch eggs and collect quail babies that follow you. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <i>The more you have the harder it is to not get hit!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Can you keep them safe?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398430/extras/cecefc92cee5dabd7dca209178d31741.poster.avif?t=1762781813\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398430/extras/cecefc92cee5dabd7dca209178d31741.webm?t=1762781813\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398430/extras/cecefc92cee5dabd7dca209178d31741.mp4?t=1762781813\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Travel across various levels with unique obstacles and challenges to overcome! <br><br><strong>Dash</strong> to get across roads faster, but be careful, if you dash too much your quail will panic! <br><br>You can also use your quail's <strong>Call</strong> ability to bring your babies closer to you and out of harm's way. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <strong>Collect hats and earn high scores!</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398430/extras/e974c31c348a129a4a6f8709dfead81e.poster.avif?t=1762781813\" width=300 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398430/extras/e974c31c348a129a4a6f8709dfead81e.webm?t=1762781813\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398430/extras/e974c31c348a129a4a6f8709dfead81e.mp4?t=1762781813\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn an award for the amount of quail you rescue and collect cosmetic hats! Reach new high scores and earn Steam Achievements.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Retro gameplay, Retro difficulty!</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398430/extras/ce2b3349be9825e54b525cf17a3b067b.poster.avif?t=1762781813\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398430/extras/ce2b3349be9825e54b525cf17a3b067b.webm?t=1762781813\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398430/extras/ce2b3349be9825e54b525cf17a3b067b.mp4?t=1762781813\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Scurry across multiple lanes of traffic, hatch eggs and collect quail babies that follow you. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <i>The more you have the harder it is to not get hit!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Can you keep them safe?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398430/extras/cecefc92cee5dabd7dca209178d31741.poster.avif?t=1762781813\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398430/extras/cecefc92cee5dabd7dca209178d31741.webm?t=1762781813\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398430/extras/cecefc92cee5dabd7dca209178d31741.mp4?t=1762781813\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Travel across various levels with unique obstacles and challenges to overcome! <br><br><strong>Dash</strong> to get across roads faster, but be careful, if you dash too much your quail will panic! <br><br>You can also use your quail's <strong>Call</strong> ability to bring your babies closer to you and out of harm's way. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <strong>Collect hats and earn high scores!</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398430/extras/e974c31c348a129a4a6f8709dfead81e.poster.avif?t=1762781813\" width=300 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398430/extras/e974c31c348a129a4a6f8709dfead81e.webm?t=1762781813\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3398430/extras/e974c31c348a129a4a6f8709dfead81e.mp4?t=1762781813\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn an award for the amount of quail you rescue and collect cosmetic hats! Reach new high scores and earn Steam Achievements.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
